summary: I want to wear his initial
body:
I want to wear his initial

On a chain round my neck, chain round my neck

Not because he owns me

But ‘cause he really knows me

Which is more than they can say, I

I recall late November, holdin’ my breath

Slowly I said, “You don’t need to save me

But would you run away with me?”

I  was having a shitty day, shitty week... Well a shitty month to be honest!
BUT FINALLY THIS CAME TO ME
AFTER A MONTH...
body:
I was having a shitty day, shitty week… Well a shitty month to be honest!

BUT FINALLY THIS CAME TO ME

AFTER A MONTH WAITING

I’m not joking when I say that Taylor is really here when I need her

Most people won’t understand but this is why I love this woman, somehow she always brightens my life 💖

Thank you @taylorswift
